refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 mixedhrtime
 boolget_as_number&false;


 Returns the system's high resolution time, counted from an arbitrary point in time.
 The delivered timestamp is monotonic and can not be adjusted.

&reftitle.parameters;
get_as_number
Whether the high resolution time should be returned as array or number.

  &reftitle.examples;



    hrtime usage


<?php
echo hrtime(true), PHP_EOL;
print_r(hrtime());
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


10444739687370679
Array
(
    [0] => 10444739
    [1] => 687464812
)
